front.title: •Dr. Chelli Lona Aphra
front.gametext: Adds 1 to power of anything she pilots. Deploys free to an unoccupied site. Your droids are deploy -1 here. When deployed, may search your Lost Pile and move one card there to the top of that pile (if that card is a droid, may retrieve it into hand).
front.lore: Female information broker, spy, and thief. Trade Federation.
